Q4. Pointers \verb!p!, \verb!q!, and \verb!r! point
to integer values \verb!3!, \verb!4!, \verb!5!
respectively.
Write down the output of the following print statement 
or write ERROR if there is a program error.
\begin{console}
p = q;
*p = 1;
std::cout << *p + *q + *r << '\n';
\end{console}
\vspace{-0.2in}
\begin{python}
from latextool_basic import consolegrid
print consolegrid()
\end{python}
